  <brief_title>HEARD (Long Term) Study - Histology of the Esophagus in Acid-Related Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Parallel-Group, Multi-Centre Study to Determine the Effect of Treatment With Esomeprazole for Six Months on Histological Markers of Esophageal Epithelial Acid-Related Disease in Patients With Upper GI Symptoms.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>AstraZeneca</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>AstraZeneca</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Determine if different levels of acid-suppression with esomeprazole for 6 months on chosen
      histological markers of esophageal epithelial acid-related disease in patients with upper GI
      symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
